Interface PointerFilter

Method Detail

accept

boolean accept(WordNetFile.Pointer pointer,
               WordSenseWrapper source)
Determine whether to accept the given pointer for expansion from the source word sense wrapper.

Note that this filter is applied before expanding a word sense.

accept

boolean accept(WordSenseWrapper expanded,
               WordSenseWrapper source)
Determine whether to accept the given expansion from the source word sense.

Note that this filter is applied to a successful expansion as a further restriction on final results.
